source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_TALK_ACTOR_02<tab>...<var 29 EA02 /var>, was it? If that is your desire, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, then it shall be done.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_TALK_ACTOR_02<tab>Oh, vous voulez mettre <var 29 EA02 /var> à la retraite<var 1D /var>?

source:
TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_Q1Retire ?
※Retired chocobos cannot be re-registered as race chocobos.
target:
TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_Q1Voulez-vous mettre à la retraite?
Note: un chocobo mis à la retraite ne pourra plus jamais être réinscrit comme animal de course.

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_A1<tab>Yes
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_A1<tab>Oui

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_A2<tab>No
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_A2<tab>Non

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_01<tab>I see you are resolved. Very well. What parting words have you for your chocobo?
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_01<tab>Je vois que votre décision est prise. Vous avez quelque chose à lui dire pour l'occasion, tout de même<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_02<tab>Praising a chocobo's acquired ability will transform it into a hereditary ability, which can be passed down through generations.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_001_02<tab>Les mots que vous prononcerez détermineront l'aptitude héréditaire qui sera inscrite dans le pedigree du chocobo.

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_Q1<tab>What will you say?
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_Q1<tab>Que voulez-vous lui dire<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_A1<tab>That'll do, chocobo. That'll do.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_A1<tab>Remercier l'animal pour ses efforts continus.

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_A2<tab>Fare thee well, old friend. I'll never forget you─nor your mastery of <var 28 ((ChocoboRaceAbility)) E80201 /var>, and how it carried us to victory!
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_A2<tab>Louer son aptitude “<var 28 ((ChocoboRaceAbility)) E80201 /var>”.

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_A3<tab>No, not yet! I am not ready to say good-bye!
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_A3<tab>Annuler

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_01<tab>...Your chocobo shall enjoy a life of luxury─of that you can be assured.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_01<tab>Bien, tout est en règle. Prenez ce certificat, il vous servira si vous souhaitez l'accoupler par la suite.

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_02<tab>As a reminder, take care not to misplace your retired chocobo registration form.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_02<tab>Un chocobo à la retraite peut s'accoupler et avoir un petit.

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_03<tab>Should you wish to arrange a covering, you will need to present it to Katering at Moogle's Gift Mounts.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_002_03<tab>Pour cela, apportez son certificat de chocobo à la retraite à Katering, au ranch de Brancharquée.

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_003_01<tab>Very well. You needn't concern yourself with this one any longer.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_RETIRE_003_01<tab>Voici venu le moment de vos adieux<var 1D /var>! Ne vous en faites pas, on va bien s'occuper de lui à partir de maintenant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_ERROR_001_01<tab>Begging your pardons, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, but your hands seem rather full at the moment. Mayhap you should see to your possessions before discussing this matter with me.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_ERROR_001_01<tab>Hum, votre inventaire est plein, on dirait<var 1D /var>! Réglez ça et revenez me voir, vous voulez bien<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_ERROR_001_02<tab>You cannot retire a chocobo without space in your inventory to store the retired chocobo registration form.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_ERROR_001_02<tab>Vous devez avoir au moins un espace libre dans votre inventaire pour recevoir le certificat de mise à la retraite.

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_TALK_ACTOR<tab>If that is your desire, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, then it shall be done.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_TALK_ACTOR<tab>Alors comme ça, vous voulez mettre votre chocobo à la retraite après tous ses bons et loyaux services<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_ERROR_002_01<tab>How odd. You did say you wished to retire a chocobo, did you not? Yet according to my records, you do not have a race chocobo registered.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_ERROR_002_01<tab>... Tiens<var 1D /var>? Mais vous n'avez pas de chocobo inscrit au registre des courses<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_ERROR_002_02<tab>Only a registered race chocobo with a rank of 40 or higher can be retired.
target: TEXT_CMNGSCCHOCOBORACERETIRE_00232_ERROR_002_02<tab>Vous pouvez uniquement mettre à la retraite un animal inscrit comme chocobo de course.
